[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯]]在[[2015年澳大利亞大獎賽|澳洲]]分佔一、二名完賽，領先第三的[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]半分鐘之久，並帶著的鉅額積分來到賽季的第二站。許多評論家在見證他們的統治性表現後，表示擔心這項運動在整個[[2015年世界一级方程式锦标赛|2015年賽季]]恐怕會更加片面且無趣，步上去年的後塵。<ref>{{cite web |title=Lewis Hamilton and Mercedes dominance 'not healthy for F1' |url=https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/news/formula-1-mercedes-making-f1-boring-rivals-fear-101157334--f1.html |website=Yahoo! Sport UK & Ireland |publisher=Eurosport |accessdate=2015-04-12 |date=2015-03-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324183742/https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/news/formula-1-mercedes-making-f1-boring-rivals-fear-101157334--f1.html |archivedate=2015-03-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title = Are Mercedes making F1 boring? Rivals fear so|url = http://www.gulf-times.com/Mobile/Sport/192/details/430938/Are-Mercedes-making-F1-boring%3F-Rivals-fear-so|publisher = Gulf Times|accessdate = 2015-04-12|date = 2015-03-15|archive-date = 2015-07-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150702204544/http://www.gulf-times.com/Mobile/Sport/192/details/430938/Are-Mercedes-making-F1-boring?-Rivals-fear-so|dead-url = yes}}</ref>[[紅牛車隊|紅牛]]車隊主席[[克里斯蒂安·霍納|克里斯蒂安·霍納]]呼籲[[國際汽聯|國際汽聯]]應介入並調整相關規則，以使比賽水平達到一致，並說道：「在規則內，國際汽聯有一套均衡機制，這正是我們所關注的。」<ref name="15 March 2015">{{cite web|last1 = Weaver|first1 = Paul|title = Red Bull’s Christian Horner asks FIA for help to save F1 season|url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/15/red-bull-christian-horner-fia-f1-season|website = guardian.co.uk|publisher = The Guardian|accessdate = 2015-04-12|archive-date = 2015-03-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150325140137/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/15/red-bull-christian-horner-fia-f1-season|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1 = Edmondson|first1 = Laurence|title = Horner calls on FIA to rein in Mercedes|url = http://en.espn.co.uk/f1/motorsport/story/194721.html|website = espn.co.uk|publisher = ESPN|accessdate = 2015-04-12|date = 2015-03-15|archive-date = 2016-02-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204201319/http://en.espn.co.uk/f1/motorsport/story/194721.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref>紅牛隨後威脅如果沒有任何新措施的話，就要離開這項運動。<ref name="telegraph1">{{cite web|last1 = Brown|first1 = Oliver|title = Red Bull's threat to quit Formula One in face of Mercedes dominance leaves a sour taste|url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11481197/Red-Bulls-threat-to-quit-Formula-One-in-face-of-Mercedes-dominance-leaves-a-sour-taste.html|website = telegraph.co.uk|publisher = The Telegraph|accessdate = 2015-04-12|date = 2015-03-18|archive-date = 2015-04-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411145032/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11481197/Red-Bulls-threat-to-quit-Formula-One-in-face-of-Mercedes-dominance-leaves-a-sour-taste.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>然而，許多評論家指出，紅牛已經享有前幾年的霸主地位， <ref name="telegraph1" />一級方程式賽車掌門人[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]表示他能理解該隊的感受，說道：「這起事件中有一項（前主席）{{Le|馬克斯·莫斯利|Max Mosley|馬克斯}}在位時推出的規則……當有一支特定車隊或引擎供應商佔盡上風──正如現在的梅賽德斯──國際汽聯能夠插手使比賽平衡。他們（梅賽德斯）有眾所認同的一流表現。我們需要對現狀做出一點改變，盡量讓比賽能夠趨於平衡。」<ref>{{cite web|title = Red Bull right to be upset by Mercedes dominance and something should be done, says F1 chief Bernie Ecclestone|url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11475233/Red-Bull-right-to-be-upset-by-Mercedes-dominance-and-something-should-be-done-says-F1-chief-Bernie-Ecclestone.html|website = telegraph.co.uk|publisher = The Telegraph|accessdate = 2015-04-12|date = 2015-03-16|archive-date = 2015-04-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411145051/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11475233/Red-Bull-right-to-be-upset-by-Mercedes-dominance-and-something-should-be-done-says-F1-chief-Bernie-Ecclestone.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>梅賽德斯執行董事{{Le|托托·沃爾夫|Toto Wolff}}對此做出回應，敦促他的對手「你他媽的就埋頭苦幹並努力整理出頭緒來」。<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Parkes|first1 = Ian|title = Toto Wolff tells critics to Mercedes dominance to 'get your f*****g head down and work to sort it out'|url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-2995930/Toto-Wolff-tells-critics-Mercedes-dominance-f-g-head-work-sort-out.html|website = dailymail.co.uk|publisher = Daily Mail|accessdate = 2015-04-12|date = 2015-03-15|archive-date = 2015-03-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150325005324/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-2995930/Toto-Wolff-tells-critics-Mercedes-dominance-f-g-head-work-sort-out.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫]]車手[[簡森·巴頓|簡森·巴頓]]則是對改變規則的成效提出質疑，說「這並沒有真正的壓制到梅賽德斯，因為他們看上去並不像在做其他車隊無法辦到的事。」<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Weaver|first1 = Paul|title = Lewis Hamilton laughs off worries over dominant Mercedes ruining F1 season|url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/16/lewis-hamilton-red-bull-mercedes-f1|website = guardian.co.uk|publisher = The Guardian|accessdate = 2015-04-12|date = 2015-03-16|archive-date = 2015-04-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150424142424/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/16/lewis-hamilton-red-bull-mercedes-f1|dead-url = no}}</ref>{{Quote box
 |quote = 「你們這群該死的人一直在抱怨著這一切，所以聽清楚了。如果你在我這個位子上，除了逃避之外，你還會做什麼？」|source = [[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]，與馬來西亞的記者談論一級方程式賽車出現的問題。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Weaver|first1=Paul|title=Malaysia Grand Prix: floundering F1 chief has few answers to myriad problems|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/27/malaysia-grand-prix-f1-bernie-ecclestone-problems|website=guardian.co.uk|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-04-12|date=2015-03-27|archive-date=2015-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329075557/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/27/malaysia-grand-prix-f1-bernie-ecclestone-problems|dead-url=no}}</ref>|width = 25%|align = right}}

在紅牛的指責後，引擎供應商[[雷諾車隊|雷諾]]的未來也成為了一個具有爭議的問題。當雷諾考慮退出這項運動時，媒體把焦點轉向他們有可能會收購[[紅牛二隊|紅牛二隊]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Renault threaten to quit F1 following criticism of their engine by Red Bull|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/27/formula-one-2015-renault-quit-red-bull|website=guardian.co.uk|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-04-12|date=2015-03-27|archive-date=2015-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406190110/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/mar/27/formula-one-2015-renault-quit-red-bull|dead-url=no}}</ref>在消息指出[[德國大獎賽|德國大獎賽]]因為缺乏資金將會退出2015年賽曆後，關於這項運動未來性的議題也更加高漲。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barretto|first1=Lawrence|title=German Grand Prix officially cancelled from 2015 Formula 1 calendar|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/118146|website=autosport.com|accessdate=2015-04-12|date=2015-03-20|archive-date=2015-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150323235829/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/118146|dead-url=yes}}</ref>其中一場最傳統的賽車賽事停辦，造成多數人提出疑問指向同為傳統賽道的[[國立蒙札賽車場|蒙札]]是否也會面臨同樣的命運。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Collantine|first1=Keith|title=Germany loses its F1 race – and Italy could be next|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/04/07/germany-loses-its-f1-race-and-italy-could-be-next/|publisher=F1Fanatic|accessdate=2015-04-12|date=2015-04-07|archive-date=2015-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411024334/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/04/07/germany-loses-its-f1-race-and-italy-could-be-next/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

